hadiths[164]{hadithnumber,text}:
4710,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kaee saal key sodey sey mana farmaya.
4711,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kaee saal tak key liye sodey sey mana farmaya hai.
4712,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kaee saal tak key liye sodey sey mana farmaya hai.
4713,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key jism mubarak par qatar basti ki bani hui do moti chadaren thin. jab aap bethtey to un mein paseena aa jata jis sey wo bojhal ho jatin. falan Yahudi key yahan Sham sey kapdey aaye to mainey kaha : agar aap us ko pegham bhej kar do kapdey udhaar kharid lein ke jab sahulat hogi to raqam dey dunga (to achchhi baat hai). aap ney usey pegham bheja to wo kehney laga : main janta hun (Hazrat ) Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka kya irada hai? wo meri raqam dabaana chahtey hain ya ye chadaren muft mein lena chahtey hain. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo jhoot boltaa hai. us ko dil mein yaqin hai ke main sab logon sey badh kar Allah Taala sey darney wala aur sab sey badh kar amanat ada karney wala hun.
4714,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key jism mubarak par qatar basti ki bani hui do moti chadaren thin. jab aap bethtey to un mein paseena aa jata jis sey wo bojhal ho jatin. falan Yahudi key yahan Sham sey kapdey aaye to mainey kaha : agar aap us ko pegham bhej kar do kapdey udhaar kharid lein ke jab sahulat hogi to raqam dey dunga (to achchhi baat hai). aap ney usey pegham bheja to wo kehney laga : main janta hun (Hazrat ) Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka kya irada hai? wo meri raqam dabaana chahtey hain ya ye chadaren muft mein lena chahtey hain. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo jhoot boltaa hai. us ko dil mein yaqin hai ke main sab logon sey badh kar Allah Taala sey darney wala aur sab sey badh kar amanat ada karney wala hun.
4715,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada mohtaram (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney qarz ki shart par bai (soda), eik sodey mein do soodon aur ghair maqbooza chiz (jo cheez qabzey mein na ho) key munafey sey mana farmaya."
4716,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada mohtaram (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney qarz ki shart par bai (soda), eik sodey mein do soodon aur ghair maqbooza chiz (jo cheez qabzey mein na ho) key munafey sey mana farmaya."
4717,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qarz ki shart par bai (sauda), eik bai (saudey) mein do shartein aur ghair maqbooza chiz (jo cheez qabzey mein na ho) ka munafaa halal nahin."
4718,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qarz ki shart par bai (sauda), eik bai (saudey) mein do shartein aur ghair maqbooza chiz (jo cheez qabzey mein na ho) ka munafaa halal nahin."
4719,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada mohtaram ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney qarz ki shart par bai (sauda), eik bai (saudey) mein do sharton aur ghair mojud chiz ki bai aur ghair maqbooza chiz (jo cheez qabzey mein na ho) key munafey sey mana farmaya hai."
4720,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada mohtaram ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney qarz ki shart par bai (sauda), eik bai (saudey) mein do sharton aur ghair mojud chiz ki bai aur ghair maqbooza chiz (jo cheez qabzey mein na ho) key munafey sey mana farmaya hai."
4721,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik sodey mein do saudon sey mana farmaya.
4722,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik sodey mein do saudon sey mana farmaya.
4723,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney muhaaqla, mazaabna, mukhaahira aur sodey mein istisna sey mana farmaya hai siwaey iske ke wo istisna malum ho."
4724,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney muhaaqla, mazaabna, mukhaahira aur sodey mein istisna sey mana farmaya hai siwaey iske ke wo istisna malum ho."
4725,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) muhaaqla, mazaabna, mukhaahira, muaawma aur bai (saudey) mein istisna sey mana farmaya, albatta atiye key darakhton mein mazaabna (mojud phal ki bai khushk phal key sath) ki rukhsat (chhoot) di hai."
4726,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) muhaaqla, mazaabna, mukhaahira, muaawma aur bai (saudey) mein istisna sey mana farmaya, albatta atiye key darakhton mein mazaabna (mojud phal ki bai khushk phal key sath) ki rukhsat (chhoot) di hai."
4727,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs khajoor key darakhton ko pewand lagaey, phir wo darkht bech dey to unka phal pewand laganey waley ko milega, siwaey iske ke khareedney wala shart lagaey."
4728,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs khajoor key darakhton ko pewand lagaey, phir wo darkht bech dey to unka phal pewand laganey waley ko milega, siwaey iske ke khareedney wala shart lagaey."
4729,Hazrat Salim key walid mohtaram (Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs pewand laganey key baad darkht bechey to uska phal bechney waley ko milega siwaey iske ke khareedney wala shart laga ley. isi tarah jo shakhs aisa ghulam farokht karey jis key paas maal ho to us ka maal bechney waley ko milega magar ye ke kharidney wala shart laga ley.
4730,Hazrat Salim key walid mohtaram (Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs pewand laganey key baad darkht bechey to uska phal bechney waley ko milega siwaey iske ke khareedney wala shart laga ley. isi tarah jo shakhs aisa ghulam farokht karey jis key paas maal ho to us ka maal bechney waley ko milega magar ye ke kharidney wala shart laga ley.
4731,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main eik safar mein Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath tha. mera oont chalney sey aajiz aa gaya. mainey socha, usey (wahin) chhod dun. itney mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) mujhey peechhey sey aa miley. aap ney uskey liye dua bhi farmaee aur usey maara bhi. phir to wo aisey chalney laga ke (sari zindagi) kabhi aisa nahin chala tha, phir aap ney farmaya : ye oont eik auqiya (chaalis dirham) main mujhey bech dey. mainey kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : bech dey, to mainey wo oont aap ko eik oqiye mein bech diya aur mainey Madina Munawra tak sawar ho kar janey ki shart laga li. jab hum Madina Munawra pahunchey, main aap key paas oont ley kar hazir huwa aur aap sey qeemat talab ki. main qeemat ley kar wapis janey laga to aap ney mujhey wapis bula bheja aur farmaya : kya to samajhta hai ke mainey tera oont leney key liye tujhey kam qeemat di hai? apna oont bhi ley ja aur qeemat bhi."
4732,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main eik safar mein Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath tha. mera oont chalney sey aajiz aa gaya. mainey socha, usey (wahin) chhod dun. itney mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) mujhey peechhey sey aa miley. aap ney uskey liye dua bhi farmaee aur usey maara bhi. phir to wo aisey chalney laga ke (sari zindagi) kabhi aisa nahin chala tha, phir aap ney farmaya : ye oont eik auqiya (chaalis dirham) main mujhey bech dey. mainey kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : bech dey, to mainey wo oont aap ko eik oqiye mein bech diya aur mainey Madina Munawra tak sawar ho kar janey ki shart laga li. jab hum Madina Munawra pahunchey, main aap key paas oont ley kar hazir huwa aur aap sey qeemat talab ki. main qeemat ley kar wapis janey laga to aap ney mujhey wapis bula bheja aur farmaya : kya to samajhta hai ke mainey tera oont leney key liye tujhey kam qeemat di hai? apna oont bhi ley ja aur qeemat bhi."
4733,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath apney pani waley oont par eik jang mein gaya, phir unhoney lambi hadees bayan ki jis ka mafhoom ye hai ke (wapsi key doran mein) oont thak kar ruk gaya. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us ko daantaa to wo itna tez ho gaya ke sab lashkar sey aagey nikal gaya. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Jabir ! main dekh raha hun ke tera oont bahut tez ho gaya hai. mainey kaha : Allah key Rasool ! ye aap ki barkat hai. aap ney farmaya : ye mujhey bech dey. tujhey (Madina Munawra tak) sawar ho kar janey ki ijazat hogi. mainey aap ko bech diya jabkey mujhey uski sakht zarurat thi. lekin mujhey sharam mehsus hui (ke aap ko inkar karun). ghazwey ki takmil key baad jab hum Madina Munawra key qarib pahunchey to mainey aap sey jaldi janey ki ijazat talab ki. mainey kaha : Allah key Rasool ! mainey naee naee shaadi ki hai. aap ney farmaya : kanwari sey ya shohar-deeda (bewa ya talaqshuda) sey? mainey kaha : Allah key Rasool ! shohar-deeda (bewa ya talaqshuda) sey. wajeh ye hai ke (merey walid) Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) shaheed ho gaey aur wo chhoti chhoti kanwari betiyan chhod gaey. mainey napasand kiya ke main un jaisi (nojawan ladki) ley aaun, is liye mainey eik shohar-deeda (bewa ya talaqshuda) sey shaadi ki jo in ko ilm aur adab sikhaey. khair ! aap ney mujhey ijazat dey di. aap ney farmaya : sham key waqt ghar pahunch jana. jab main aaya to mainey apney mamu ko oont key farokht karney ka bataya. unhoney mujhey malamat ki. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tashrif ley aaye to main aap key paas subah key waqt oont ley kar gaya. aap ney mujhey oont ki qeemat bhi di, oont bhi diya aur logon key barabar hissa bhi diya."
4734,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath apney pani waley oont par eik jang mein gaya, phir unhoney lambi hadees bayan ki jis ka mafhoom ye hai ke (wapsi key doran mein) oont thak kar ruk gaya. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us ko daantaa to wo itna tez ho gaya ke sab lashkar sey aagey nikal gaya. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Jabir ! main dekh raha hun ke tera oont bahut tez ho gaya hai. mainey kaha : Allah key Rasool ! ye aap ki barkat hai. aap ney farmaya : ye mujhey bech dey. tujhey (Madina Munawra tak) sawar ho kar janey ki ijazat hogi. mainey aap ko bech diya jabkey mujhey uski sakht zarurat thi. lekin mujhey sharam mehsus hui (ke aap ko inkar karun). ghazwey ki takmil key baad jab hum Madina Munawra key qarib pahunchey to mainey aap sey jaldi janey ki ijazat talab ki. mainey kaha : Allah key Rasool ! mainey naee naee shaadi ki hai. aap ney farmaya : kanwari sey ya shohar-deeda (bewa ya talaqshuda) sey? mainey kaha : Allah key Rasool ! shohar-deeda (bewa ya talaqshuda) sey. wajeh ye hai ke (merey walid) Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) shaheed ho gaey aur wo chhoti chhoti kanwari betiyan chhod gaey. mainey napasand kiya ke main un jaisi (nojawan ladki) ley aaun, is liye mainey eik shohar-deeda (bewa ya talaqshuda) sey shaadi ki jo in ko ilm aur adab sikhaey. khair ! aap ney mujhey ijazat dey di. aap ney farmaya : sham key waqt ghar pahunch jana. jab main aaya to mainey apney mamu ko oont key farokht karney ka bataya. unhoney mujhey malamat ki. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tashrif ley aaye to main aap key paas subah key waqt oont ley kar gaya. aap ney mujhey oont ki qeemat bhi di, oont bhi diya aur logon key barabar hissa bhi diya."
4735,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : main eik safar mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath tha. main eik oont par sawar tha. aap ney farmaya : kya baat hai to sab sey aakhir mein hai? mainey kaha : mera oont chalney sey aajiz aa chuka hai. aap ney uski dum pakad kar usey daantaa. phir to wo itna aagey chala gaya ke mujhey us ka sar sambhalna mushkil ho raha tha. jab hum Madina Munawra key qarib huye to aap ney farmaya : terey oont ka kya haal hai? ye mujhey bech dey. mainey kaha : ye wesey hi aap ka hai. (bechney ki kya zarurat hai?) aap ney farmaya : nahin mujhey bech dey. mainey kaha : nahin, balke ye wesey hi aap ka hai. aap ney farmaya : nahin balke mujhey bech dey. mainey ye eik oqiye mein de diya. haan to sawar reh, phir jab to Madiney pahunch jaey to usey merey paas ley aana. phir jab main Madina Munawra mein aaya to main oont ley kar aap key paas gaya. aap ney Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya : Bilal ! is ko to eik auqiya (chaalis darhum) tol dey aur eik qeeraat is ko zayed dey dey. mainey kaha : ye qeeraat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey zayed diya hai, ye kabhi bhi mujh sey juda nahin hoga. mainey usey eik thaili mein dal liya. wo hamesha merey paas raha yahan tak ke Harra waley din Sham waley aaye to unhoney hum sey jo chaha, loot liya."
4736,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : main eik safar mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath tha. main eik oont par sawar tha. aap ney farmaya : kya baat hai to sab sey aakhir mein hai? mainey kaha : mera oont chalney sey aajiz aa chuka hai. aap ney uski dum pakad kar usey daantaa. phir to wo itna aagey chala gaya ke mujhey us ka sar sambhalna mushkil ho raha tha. jab hum Madina Munawra key qarib huye to aap ney farmaya : terey oont ka kya haal hai? ye mujhey bech dey. mainey kaha : ye wesey hi aap ka hai. (bechney ki kya zarurat hai?) aap ney farmaya : nahin mujhey bech dey. mainey kaha : nahin, balke ye wesey hi aap ka hai. aap ney farmaya : nahin balke mujhey bech dey. mainey ye eik oqiye mein de diya. haan to sawar reh, phir jab to Madiney pahunch jaey to usey merey paas ley aana. phir jab main Madina Munawra mein aaya to main oont ley kar aap key paas gaya. aap ney Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya : Bilal ! is ko to eik auqiya (chaalis darhum) tol dey aur eik qeeraat is ko zayed dey dey. mainey kaha : ye qeeraat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey zayed diya hai, ye kabhi bhi mujh sey juda nahin hoga. mainey usey eik thaili mein dal liya. wo hamesha merey paas raha yahan tak ke Harra waley din Sham waley aaye to unhoney hum sey jo chaha, loot liya."
4737,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) mujhey miley to main apney eik pani bharney waley bad-mizaaj oont par sawar tha. mainey (afsos kartey huye) kaha : afsos ! pani ka nikamma oont hamesha hamarey paas rehta hai. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey Jabir ! kya to mujhey ye oont farokht kerega? mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! ye wesey hi aap ki khidmat mein pesh hai. aap ney dua di : aey Allah ! is ko maaf farma. is par reham farma. phir farmaya : mainey ye itney itney mein kharid liya. wesey main Madina Munawra tak iski sawari ki tujhey ijazat deta hun. jab main Madina Munawra pahuncha to mainey us oont ko tayyar kiya aur aap key paas ley gaya. aap ney farmaya : Bilal ! isko is oont ki qeemat dey do. jab main wapis muda to mujhey bulaya. mujhey khatra huwa ke aap oont wapis farma dengey. aap ney farmaya : ye oont tera hi hai.
4738,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) mujhey miley to main apney eik pani bharney waley bad-mizaaj oont par sawar tha. mainey (afsos kartey huye) kaha : afsos ! pani ka nikamma oont hamesha hamarey paas rehta hai. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey Jabir ! kya to mujhey ye oont farokht kerega? mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! ye wesey hi aap ki khidmat mein pesh hai. aap ney dua di : aey Allah ! is ko maaf farma. is par reham farma. phir farmaya : mainey ye itney itney mein kharid liya. wesey main Madina Munawra tak iski sawari ki tujhey ijazat deta hun. jab main Madina Munawra pahuncha to mainey us oont ko tayyar kiya aur aap key paas ley gaya. aap ney farmaya : Bilal ! isko is oont ki qeemat dey do. jab main wapis muda to mujhey bulaya. mujhey khatra huwa ke aap oont wapis farma dengey. aap ney farmaya : ye oont tera hi hai.
4739,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath chal rahey they. main apney pani dhoney waley oont par sawar tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya to apna ye oont mujhey itney itney mein farokht kerega? Allah Taala teri maghfirat farmaey. mainey kaha : Allah key Nabi ! wo aap ka hi hai. phir farmaya : mujhey itney itney mein farokht kerega? Allah Taala teri maghfirat farmaey. mainey kaha : Allah key Nabi ! yaqinan ye aap ka hi hai. aap ney phir farmaya : to ye oont mujhey itney mein farokht kerega? Allah Taala tujhey maaf farmaey. mainey kaha : ji haan. wo aap ka hi hai. raawi Abu-Nazara ney kaha ke (Allah tujhey maaf kerey) eik kalima hai jo musalman umuman kehtey they. to ye kaam kar ley, Allah tujhey maaf kerey."
4740,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath chal rahey they. main apney pani dhoney waley oont par sawar tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya to apna ye oont mujhey itney itney mein farokht kerega? Allah Taala teri maghfirat farmaey. mainey kaha : Allah key Nabi ! wo aap ka hi hai. phir farmaya : mujhey itney itney mein farokht kerega? Allah Taala teri maghfirat farmaey. mainey kaha : Allah key Nabi ! yaqinan ye aap ka hi hai. aap ney phir farmaya : to ye oont mujhey itney mein farokht kerega? Allah Taala tujhey maaf farmaey. mainey kaha : ji haan. wo aap ka hi hai. raawi Abu-Nazara ney kaha ke (Allah tujhey maaf kerey) eik kalima hai jo musalman umuman kehtey they. to ye kaam kar ley, Allah tujhey maaf kerey."
4741,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke mainey Barira ko (us key maalikon sey) kharid to uskey maalikon ney uskey wala ki apney liye shart laga li. mainey ye baat Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey zikr ki to aap ney farmaya : usey azad kar dey. wala usi ki hoti hai jo paisey deta (ghulam ko khareedtaa) hai. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : mainey usey azad kar diya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey bulaya aur usey apney khawind key (paas rehney ya na rehney key) barey mein ikhtiyar diya. us ney khawind sey apni judai ko pasand kiya. us ka khawind azad tha.
4742,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke mainey Barira ko (us key maalikon sey) kharid to uskey maalikon ney uskey wala ki apney liye shart laga li. mainey ye baat Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey zikr ki to aap ney farmaya : usey azad kar dey. wala usi ki hoti hai jo paisey deta (ghulam ko khareedtaa) hai. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : mainey usey azad kar diya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey bulaya aur usey apney khawind key (paas rehney ya na rehney key) barey mein ikhtiyar diya. us ney khawind sey apni judai ko pasand kiya. us ka khawind azad tha.
4743,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Barira ko azad karney key liye usey khareedney ka irada kiya lekin uskey malikon ney apney liye wala ki shart laga li. unhoney ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey zikr ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : to usey kharid-kar azad kar dey. bilashuba wala usi ki hoti hai jo (ghulam ko) azad karta hai. (ye waqia bhi huwa ke) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas gosht laya gaya aur batlaya gaya ke ye gosht Barira par sadqa kiya gaya hai (aur us ney hamein bheja hai). aap ney farmaya : sadqa uskey liye hai. hamarey liye tohfa hi hai. aur usey (khawind key barey mein) ikhtiyar diya gaya.
4744,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Barira ko azad karney key liye usey khareedney ka irada kiya lekin uskey malikon ney apney liye wala ki shart laga li. unhoney ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey zikr ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : to usey kharid-kar azad kar dey. bilashuba wala usi ki hoti hai jo (ghulam ko) azad karta hai. (ye waqia bhi huwa ke) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas gosht laya gaya aur batlaya gaya ke ye gosht Barira par sadqa kiya gaya hai (aur us ney hamein bheja hai). aap ney farmaya : sadqa uskey liye hai. hamarey liye tohfa hi hai. aur usey (khawind key barey mein) ikhtiyar diya gaya.
4745,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney eik londi ko khareedney ka irada kiya. unka irada usey azad karney ka tha. us londi key maalikon ney kaha : hum londi bech detey hain magar wala ka haq hamein hasil hoga. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey zikr ki to aap ney farmaya : ye shart bai (saudey) mein rukawat nahin honi chahiye. wala usi ko milti hai jo (ghulam ko) azad karta hai.
4746,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney eik londi ko khareedney ka irada kiya. unka irada usey azad karney ka tha. us londi key maalikon ney kaha : hum londi bech detey hain magar wala ka haq hamein hasil hoga. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey zikr ki to aap ney farmaya : ye shart bai (saudey) mein rukawat nahin honi chahiye. wala usi ko milti hai jo (ghulam ko) azad karta hai.
4747,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney maale-ghanimat ki taqseem sey pehley us ka soda karney sey mana farmaya. aur (isi tarah naee khareedi hui) hamila laundiyon key sath jima (sambhog) karney sey mana farmaya yahan tak ke wo apney pet ka bachcha jann den, isi ke sath aap ney har kuchli waley darindey ka gosht khaney sey mana farmaya."
4748,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney maale-ghanimat ki taqseem sey pehley us ka soda karney sey mana farmaya. aur (isi tarah naee khareedi hui) hamila laundiyon key sath jima (sambhog) karney sey mana farmaya yahan tak ke wo apney pet ka bachcha jann den, isi ke sath aap ney har kuchli waley darindey ka gosht khaney sey mana farmaya."
4749,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : shuf'a har mushtarka (saajhey ki) chiz mein ho sakta hai. wo ghar ho ya baagh (aur khet). kisi eik shareek ko jayez nahin ke (mushtarka chiz mein apna hissa) farokht karey yahan tak ke apney shareek (sathi ya sathiyon) ko muttala (ittila) kerey. agar wo bila ittilaa farokht kar dey to shareek us ko leney ka haq-daar hoga siwaey iske ke usey ittilaa karney key baad bechey.
4750,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : shuf'a har mushtarka (saajhey ki) chiz mein ho sakta hai. wo ghar ho ya baagh (aur khet). kisi eik shareek ko jayez nahin ke (mushtarka chiz mein apna hissa) farokht karey yahan tak ke apney shareek (sathi ya sathiyon) ko muttala (ittila) kerey. agar wo bila ittilaa farokht kar dey to shareek us ko leney ka haq-daar hoga siwaey iske ke usey ittilaa karney key baad bechey.
4751,"Hazrat Ammara bin Khuzaima key chacha mohtaram sey riwayat hai, aur wo Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sahabi they, ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik erabi (dehati) sey eik ghodaa kharid aur aap usey apney sath ley gaey taake wo apney ghodey ki qeemat wasul karey. Nabi mukarram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) zara tez chal rahey they jabkey wo erabi (dehati) aahista aahista aa raha tha. log us erabi (dehati) ko rok kar us sey ghodey ka soda karney lagey. in ko ye ilm nahin tha ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) us ghodey ko kharid chukey hain, yahan tak ke kisi ney us bhaaw sey ziyada bhaaw laga diya jis par aap ka soda tey huwa tha. erabi (dehati) ney Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko buland aawaz sey pukar kar kaha : agar aap ney ye ghodaa khareednaa hai to kharid lein warna main bechney laga hun. aap ney uski aawaz suni to ruk gaey aur farmaya : main tujh sey kharid nahin chuka? us ney kaha : nahin Allah ki qism ! mainey to aap ko ye nahin bechaa. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main to isey tujh sey kharid chuka hun. log Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur erabi (dehati) key ird-gird jama honey lagey. wo dono aapas mein takraar kar rahey they. erabi (dehati) kehney laga : koi gawah pesh karen jo gawahi dey ke mainey aap ko ye ghodaa bechaa hai. Hazrat Khuzaima bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey : main gawahi deta hun ke tu ney ye ghodaa aap ko bechaa hai. (khair ! wo maamla tey ho gaya, baad mein) aap Hazrat Khuzaima (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf mutawajjeh huye aur farmaya : tum kis tarah gawahi detey ho? unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap ki tasdeeq ki bina par. tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Khuzaima (Raziallahu anhu) ki gawahi do aadmiyon key barabar qarar dey di."
4752,"Hazrat Ammara bin Khuzaima key chacha mohtaram sey riwayat hai, aur wo Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sahabi they, ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik erabi (dehati) sey eik ghodaa kharid aur aap usey apney sath ley gaey taake wo apney ghodey ki qeemat wasul karey. Nabi mukarram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) zara tez chal rahey they jabkey wo erabi (dehati) aahista aahista aa raha tha. log us erabi (dehati) ko rok kar us sey ghodey ka soda karney lagey. in ko ye ilm nahin tha ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) us ghodey ko kharid chukey hain, yahan tak ke kisi ney us bhaaw sey ziyada bhaaw laga diya jis par aap ka soda tey huwa tha. erabi (dehati) ney Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko buland aawaz sey pukar kar kaha : agar aap ney ye ghodaa khareednaa hai to kharid lein warna main bechney laga hun. aap ney uski aawaz suni to ruk gaey aur farmaya : main tujh sey kharid nahin chuka? us ney kaha : nahin Allah ki qism ! mainey to aap ko ye nahin bechaa. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main to isey tujh sey kharid chuka hun. log Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur erabi (dehati) key ird-gird jama honey lagey. wo dono aapas mein takraar kar rahey they. erabi (dehati) kehney laga : koi gawah pesh karen jo gawahi dey ke mainey aap ko ye ghodaa bechaa hai. Hazrat Khuzaima bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey : main gawahi deta hun ke tu ney ye ghodaa aap ko bechaa hai. (khair ! wo maamla tey ho gaya, baad mein) aap Hazrat Khuzaima (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf mutawajjeh huye aur farmaya : tum kis tarah gawahi detey ho? unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap ki tasdeeq ki bina par. tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Khuzaima (Raziallahu anhu) ki gawahi do aadmiyon key barabar qarar dey di."
4753,Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jab khareedney aur bechney waley ka (qeemat waghera mein) ikhtilaf ho jaey aur un mein sey kisi key paas sabut na ho to moatabar baat wo hogi jo saman ka Malik kahe ya wo soda khatam kar den.
4754,Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jab khareedney aur bechney waley ka (qeemat waghera mein) ikhtilaf ho jaey aur un mein sey kisi key paas sabut na ho to moatabar baat wo hogi jo saman ka Malik kahe ya wo soda khatam kar den.
4755,"Hazrat Abdul-Malik bin Ubaid sey riwayat hai ke hum Hazrat Abu-Ubaid bin Abdullah bin Masood ki majlis mein hazir they ke unkey paas do aadmi aaye. unhoney aapas mein kisi saman ka soda kiya tha. eik keh raha tha : mainey itney mein liya. doosra keh raha tha : mainey itney ka bechaa. Hazrat Abu-Ubaida farmaney lagey : Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aisa masla pesh huwa tha to unhoney farmaya tha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir tha key aap key paas isi qisam ka muqadma laya gaya. aap ney hukm diya ke bechney waley sey qism li jaey, phir khareedney waley ko ikhtiyar hoga, chahey us bhaaw mein ley ley ya phir soda chhod dey."
4756,"Hazrat Abdul-Malik bin Ubaid sey riwayat hai ke hum Hazrat Abu-Ubaid bin Abdullah bin Masood ki majlis mein hazir they ke unkey paas do aadmi aaye. unhoney aapas mein kisi saman ka soda kiya tha. eik keh raha tha : mainey itney mein liya. doosra keh raha tha : mainey itney ka bechaa. Hazrat Abu-Ubaida farmaney lagey : Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aisa masla pesh huwa tha to unhoney farmaya tha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir tha key aap key paas isi qisam ka muqadma laya gaya. aap ney hukm diya ke bechney waley sey qism li jaey, phir khareedney waley ko ikhtiyar hoga, chahey us bhaaw mein ley ley ya phir soda chhod dey."
4757,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik Yahudi sey udhaar ghalla kharid tha aur bator zamanat apni zireh us ko girwi mein di thi.
4758,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik Yahudi sey udhaar ghalla kharid tha aur bator zamanat apni zireh us ko girwi mein di thi.
4759,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Allah ko piyarey huye to aap ki zireh eik Yahudi key paas girwi rakhi hui thi kyonkey aap ney us sey apney ehal aur ayaal key liye tees saa ghalla (jau) udhaar liye they.
4760,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Allah ko piyarey huye to aap ki zireh eik Yahudi key paas girwi rakhi hui thi kyonkey aap ney us sey apney ehal aur ayaal key liye tees saa ghalla (jau) udhaar liye they.
4761,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Banu Azra key eik aadmi ney apna eik ghulam mudabbir kiya. ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko pahunchi to aap ney farmaya : kya terey paas iskey ilawa koi aur maal hai? us ney kaha : nahin. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kon shakhs mujh sey ye (ghulam) khareedtaa hai? Hazrat Nuaim bin Abdullah Adwi (Raziallahu anhu) ney usey aath-sau dirham mein kharid liya. wo ye raqam Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas ley kar aaye. aap ney wo uskey supurd kar di aur farmaya : pehley apney aap par kharch kar, phir agar kuchh bach jaey to wo terey ehal aur ayaal key liye hai, phir agar terey ehal aur ayaal sey kuchh bach jaey to terey rishte-daaron ka haq hai, albatta agar terey rishtey-daaron sey bhi kuchh bach jaey to aisey aisey aur aisey, yani apney aagey, apney daeyn aur apney baain (Allah key raastey mein kharch kar)."
4762,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Banu Azra key eik aadmi ney apna eik ghulam mudabbir kiya. ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko pahunchi to aap ney farmaya : kya terey paas iskey ilawa koi aur maal hai? us ney kaha : nahin. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kon shakhs mujh sey ye (ghulam) khareedtaa hai? Hazrat Nuaim bin Abdullah Adwi (Raziallahu anhu) ney usey aath-sau dirham mein kharid liya. wo ye raqam Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas ley kar aaye. aap ney wo uskey supurd kar di aur farmaya : pehley apney aap par kharch kar, phir agar kuchh bach jaey to wo terey ehal aur ayaal key liye hai, phir agar terey ehal aur ayaal sey kuchh bach jaey to terey rishte-daaron ka haq hai, albatta agar terey rishtey-daaron sey bhi kuchh bach jaey to aisey aisey aur aisey, yani apney aagey, apney daeyn aur apney baain (Allah key raastey mein kharch kar)."
4763,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke ansaar mein sey eik aadmi ney jisey Abu-Mazkoor kaha jata tha, apna eik ghulam mudabbir kiya. us ghulam ka naam Yaqub tha. us aadmi key paas koi aur maal nahin tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us ko bulaya aur farmaya : is ghulam ko kon khareedega? Hazrat Nuaim bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ney usey aath-sau dirham mein kharid liya. aap ney wo dirham uskey supurd kiye aur farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi aadmi faqir (gharib) ho to wo pehley apney aap par kharch kerey. agar kuchh bachey to apney baal-bachchon par kharch karey. mazeed agar kuchh bachey to apney qaribi aur rishtey-daaron par kharch kerey. phir agar bach jaey to phir idhar-udhar (Fi-sabililah sadqa kerey)."
4764,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke ansaar mein sey eik aadmi ney jisey Abu-Mazkoor kaha jata tha, apna eik ghulam mudabbir kiya. us ghulam ka naam Yaqub tha. us aadmi key paas koi aur maal nahin tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us ko bulaya aur farmaya : is ghulam ko kon khareedega? Hazrat Nuaim bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ney usey aath-sau dirham mein kharid liya. aap ney wo dirham uskey supurd kiye aur farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi aadmi faqir (gharib) ho to wo pehley apney aap par kharch kerey. agar kuchh bachey to apney baal-bachchon par kharch karey. mazeed agar kuchh bachey to apney qaribi aur rishtey-daaron par kharch kerey. phir agar bach jaey to phir idhar-udhar (Fi-sabililah sadqa kerey)."
4765,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik mudabbir bech diya tha.
4766,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik mudabbir bech diya tha.
4767,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Barira Aaisha key paas aai. wo apni kitaabat key barey mein un sey kuch madad ki talabgar thi. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney usey farmaya : apney malikon key paas ja, agar wo razi hon ke main teri taraf sey kitaabat ki puri raqam yakmusht ada kar dun aur to meri taraf sey azad ho jaey to main tayyar hun. Barira ney ye baat apney maalikon sey zikr ki to unhoney inkar kar diya. aur kehney lagey : agar wo tujhey azad kar key sawab hasil karna chahti hain to badi khushi sey karen lekin wala ka haq hamara hoga. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey zikr ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : to kharid kar azad kar dey. wala ka haq usi ka hai jo azad kerey. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (khutbey mein) farmaya : un logon ka kya haal hai jo aisi sharten lagatey hain jo kitabullah ki taraf sey jayez nahin. jo shakhs bhi aisi shart lagata hai, jo kitabullah ki taraf sey jayez nahin, wo shart uskey haq mein nahin maana jaeygi, chahey chaahey sau dafa shart laga ley. Allah Taala ki nafiz karda shart (hukm) ziyada moatabar aur mazbut hai."
4768,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Barira Aaisha key paas aai. wo apni kitaabat key barey mein un sey kuch madad ki talabgar thi. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney usey farmaya : apney malikon key paas ja, agar wo razi hon ke main teri taraf sey kitaabat ki puri raqam yakmusht ada kar dun aur to meri taraf sey azad ho jaey to main tayyar hun. Barira ney ye baat apney maalikon sey zikr ki to unhoney inkar kar diya. aur kehney lagey : agar wo tujhey azad kar key sawab hasil karna chahti hain to badi khushi sey karen lekin wala ka haq hamara hoga. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey zikr ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : to kharid kar azad kar dey. wala ka haq usi ka hai jo azad kerey. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (khutbey mein) farmaya : un logon ka kya haal hai jo aisi sharten lagatey hain jo kitabullah ki taraf sey jayez nahin. jo shakhs bhi aisi shart lagata hai, jo kitabullah ki taraf sey jayez nahin, wo shart uskey haq mein nahin maana jaeygi, chahey chaahey sau dafa shart laga ley. Allah Taala ki nafiz karda shart (hukm) ziyada moatabar aur mazbut hai."
4769,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Barira merey paas aai aur kehney lagi : aey Aaisha ! mainey apney maalikon sey nau oqiye par azadi ka muahida kiya hai. har saal eik auqiya dena hoga, lihaza meri madad farmaiye. abhi tak us ney apni kitaabat ki raqam sey kuchh bhi ada nahin kiya tha. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney chaha ke wo usey azad kar den, is liye unhoney us sey kaha : apney malikon key paas jaao agar wo pasand karen ke main in ko ye (un ki raqam) yakmusht ada kar dun aur teri wala main lungi to main aisa karney ko tayyar hun. Hazrat Barira (Raziallahu anha) apney malikon key paas gaee aur ye baat unhein pesh ki. unhoney inkar kiya aur kehney lagey : agar wo sawab hasil karney key liye tujhey azad karna chahen to kar den lekin wala hamari hogi. Hazrat Barira ney ye baat Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anhu) sey zikr ki aur Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey zikr ki. aap ney farmaya : un ki is baat ki wajeh se inkar na karna balke kharid kar azad kar do. wala usi ki hoti hai jo azad kerey. unhoney aisey hi kiya. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) logon mein khutba deney key liye khadey huye. aap ney Allah Taala ki hamd aur sanaa bayan farmaee, phir farmaya : amma'-baad ! kya wajeh hai ke log saudey kartey waqt aisi sharten lagatey hain jo kitabullah ki taraf sey jayez nahin? jo shakhs bhi aisi shart lagaeyga jo kitabullah ki taraf sey jayez na ho to wo batil aur mardud hogi agar-che sau dafa lagai gaee ho. Allah Taala ka faisla hi sahih hai aur Allah Taala ki jayez karda shartein hi moatabar hain. yad rakho ! wala usi ki hogi jo azad kerega."
4770,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Barira merey paas aai aur kehney lagi : aey Aaisha ! mainey apney maalikon sey nau oqiye par azadi ka muahida kiya hai. har saal eik auqiya dena hoga, lihaza meri madad farmaiye. abhi tak us ney apni kitaabat ki raqam sey kuchh bhi ada nahin kiya tha. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney chaha ke wo usey azad kar den, is liye unhoney us sey kaha : apney malikon key paas jaao agar wo pasand karen ke main in ko ye (un ki raqam) yakmusht ada kar dun aur teri wala main lungi to main aisa karney ko tayyar hun. Hazrat Barira (Raziallahu anha) apney malikon key paas gaee aur ye baat unhein pesh ki. unhoney inkar kiya aur kehney lagey : agar wo sawab hasil karney key liye tujhey azad karna chahen to kar den lekin wala hamari hogi. Hazrat Barira ney ye baat Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anhu) sey zikr ki aur Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey zikr ki. aap ney farmaya : un ki is baat ki wajeh se inkar na karna balke kharid kar azad kar do. wala usi ki hoti hai jo azad kerey. unhoney aisey hi kiya. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) logon mein khutba deney key liye khadey huye. aap ney Allah Taala ki hamd aur sanaa bayan farmaee, phir farmaya : amma'-baad ! kya wajeh hai ke log saudey kartey waqt aisi sharten lagatey hain jo kitabullah ki taraf sey jayez nahin? jo shakhs bhi aisi shart lagaeyga jo kitabullah ki taraf sey jayez na ho to wo batil aur mardud hogi agar-che sau dafa lagai gaee ho. Allah Taala ka faisla hi sahih hai aur Allah Taala ki jayez karda shartein hi moatabar hain. yad rakho ! wala usi ki hogi jo azad kerega."
4771,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney wala key bechney aur hiba karney sey mana farmaya hai.
4772,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney wala key bechney aur hiba karney sey mana farmaya hai.
