4774,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney wala ko bechney aur hiba karney sey mana farmaya hai.
4775,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney wala ko bechney aur hiba karney sey mana farmaya hai.
4776,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney wala ko bechney aur hiba karney sey mana farmaya hai.
4777,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney pani bechney sey mana farmaya hai.
4778,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney pani bechney sey mana farmaya hai.
4779,Hazrat Ayaas bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko pani ki farokht sey mana farmatey suna. ustaad Quteba ney kaha ke main us (ustaad Sufiyan bin uena) sey Abu-Minhaal key baaz huroof is tarah nahin samajh saka jis tarah main chahta tha.
4780,Hazrat Ayaas bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko pani ki farokht sey mana farmatey suna. ustaad Quteba ney kaha ke main us (ustaad Sufiyan bin uena) sey Abu-Minhaal key baaz huroof is tarah nahin samajh saka jis tarah main chahta tha.
4781,Hazrat Ayaas sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney zayed pani bechney sey mana farmaya hai. (Hazrat Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ki zamin ) wahat key naazim ney wahat ka zayed pani bechaa to Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ney isey napasand farmaya.
4782,Hazrat Ayaas sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney zayed pani bechney sey mana farmaya hai. (Hazrat Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ki zamin ) wahat key naazim ney wahat ka zayed pani bechaa to Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ney isey napasand farmaya.
4783,Sahabi Rasool Hazrat Ayaas bin Abd (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke zayed pani na becho kyonkey Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney faaltu pani bechney sey mana farmaya hai.
4784,Sahabi Rasool Hazrat Ayaas bin Abd (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke zayed pani na becho kyonkey Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney faaltu pani bechney sey mana farmaya hai.
4785,"Hazrat ibn Waleh Misri sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey angoor key nichodey huye joos key barey mein puchha to Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : eik aadmi ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein oont par ladi hui sharab key do mishkeezey bator tohfa pesh kiye. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey farmaya : tujhey ilm nahin ke Allah ney sharab haram farma di hai? us ney apney pehlu mein (bethey ya khadey huye) eik shakhs sey aahista sey kuchh kaha aur jo kuchh us ney kaha, usey main is tarah nahin samajh saka jis tarah main chahta tha, lihaza mainey (us ki baabat haazirin mein sey kisi sey) puchha. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us sey puchha : tu ney aahista sey us ko kya kaha hai? us ney kaha : mainey usey sharab farokht karney ko kaha hai. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis zaat ney sharab ko haram qarar diya hai, us ney us ko bechnaa bhi haram kiya hai. us shakhs ney dono mishkeezon key munh khol diye yahan tak ke jo kuchh sharab is mein thi beh gaee."
4786,"Hazrat ibn Waleh Misri sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey angoor key nichodey huye joos key barey mein puchha to Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : eik aadmi ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein oont par ladi hui sharab key do mishkeezey bator tohfa pesh kiye. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey farmaya : tujhey ilm nahin ke Allah ney sharab haram farma di hai? us ney apney pehlu mein (bethey ya khadey huye) eik shakhs sey aahista sey kuchh kaha aur jo kuchh us ney kaha, usey main is tarah nahin samajh saka jis tarah main chahta tha, lihaza mainey (us ki baabat haazirin mein sey kisi sey) puchha. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us sey puchha : tu ney aahista sey us ko kya kaha hai? us ney kaha : mainey usey sharab farokht karney ko kaha hai. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis zaat ney sharab ko haram qarar diya hai, us ney us ko bechnaa bhi haram kiya hai. us shakhs ney dono mishkeezon key munh khol diye yahan tak ke jo kuchh sharab is mein thi beh gaee."
4787,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke jab sood ki (hurmat ki) aayaat utri to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) member par tashrif farma huye aur ye aayaat logon ko padh kar sunaeen, phir aap ney sharab ki tijarat ko bhi haram qarar diya."
4788,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke jab sood ki (hurmat ki) aayaat utri to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) member par tashrif farma huye aur ye aayaat logon ko padh kar sunaeen, phir aap ney sharab ki tijarat ko bhi haram qarar diya."
4789,"Hazrat abu-Masood Aqba bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kuttey ki qeemat , zaaniya ki ujrat aur (ghaib ki khabren bataaney waley) kaahin ki sheerni aur kamai (nazar aur niyaz) sey mana farmaya hai."
4790,"Hazrat abu-Masood Aqba bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kuttey ki qeemat , zaaniya ki ujrat aur (ghaib ki khabren bataaney waley) kaahin ki sheerni aur kamai (nazar aur niyaz) sey mana farmaya hai."
4791,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney bahut si chizon ko haram qarar detey huye farmaya : aur kuttey ki qeemat (bhi haram hai).
4792,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney bahut si chizon ko haram qarar detey huye farmaya : aur kuttey ki qeemat (bhi haram hai).
4793,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kuttey aur billi ki qeemat sey mana farmaya, albatta shikari kuttey ko mustashnaa (apwaad) farmaya. Abu-Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) farmatey hain ke ye hadees munkir hai."
4794,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kuttey aur billi ki qeemat sey mana farmaya, albatta shikari kuttey ko mustashnaa (apwaad) farmaya. Abu-Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) farmatey hain ke ye hadees munkir hai."
4795,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko fateh Makka key saal Makka Mukarrama mein farmatey suna : Allah Taala aur uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney sharab , murdar , khinzir aur buton ki kharid aur farokht haram qarar di hai. aap sey puchha gaya : Allah key Rasool ! zara murdar ki charbi key barey mein irshad farmaeyn? uskey sath kashtiyan lep ki jati hain. aur ye chamdey ko mali jati hai aur log us sey roshni hasil kartey hain. aap ney farmaya : nahin, ye haram hai. us waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ye bhi farmaya : Allah Taala yahudiyon par lanat farmaai ke Allah ney jab un par charbi haram farma di to unhoney usey pighla kar bechaa aur uski qeemat khai."
4796,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko fateh Makka key saal Makka Mukarrama mein farmatey suna : Allah Taala aur uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney sharab , murdar , khinzir aur buton ki kharid aur farokht haram qarar di hai. aap sey puchha gaya : Allah key Rasool ! zara murdar ki charbi key barey mein irshad farmaeyn? uskey sath kashtiyan lep ki jati hain. aur ye chamdey ko mali jati hai aur log us sey roshni hasil kartey hain. aap ney farmaya : nahin, ye haram hai. us waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ye bhi farmaya : Allah Taala yahudiyon par lanat farmaai ke Allah ney jab un par charbi haram farma di to unhoney usey pighla kar bechaa aur uski qeemat khai."
4797,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney oont ki jufti, (zayed) pani aur kaasht kaari key liye zamin ki farokht sey mana farmaya ke eik aadmi apni zamin aur us ka pani kisi ko bech dey. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us sey mana farmaya hai."
4798,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney oont ki jufti, (zayed) pani aur kaasht kaari key liye zamin ki farokht sey mana farmaya ke eik aadmi apni zamin aur us ka pani kisi ko bech dey. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us sey mana farmaya hai."
4799,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney nar ki jufti ki ujrat sey mana farmaya hai.
4800,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney nar ki jufti ki ujrat sey mana farmaya hai.
4801,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : banu Kilaab key eik (chhotey) qabiley banu Sa'aq ka eik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur aap sey nar ki jufti ki ujrat key barey mein puchha. aap ney usey is sey mana farmaya. us ney kaha : kabhi-kabhi us (jufti) par hum khushi sey kuchh dey detey hain (to aap ney iski rukhsat (chhoot) farma di).
4802,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : banu Kilaab key eik (chhotey) qabiley banu Sa'aq ka eik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur aap sey nar ki jufti ki ujrat key barey mein puchha. aap ney usey is sey mana farmaya. us ney kaha : kabhi-kabhi us (jufti) par hum khushi sey kuchh dey detey hain (to aap ney iski rukhsat (chhoot) farma di).
4803,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney singi laganey waley ki kamai, kuttey ki farokht aur nar ki jufti ki ujrat sey mana farmaya hai."
4804,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney singi laganey waley ki kamai, kuttey ki farokht aur nar ki jufti ki ujrat sey mana farmaya hai."
4805,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney nar ki jufti ki ujrat sey mana farmaya.
4806,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney nar ki jufti ki ujrat sey mana farmaya.
4807,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kuttey ki qeemat aur nar ki jufti ki ujrat leney sey mana farmaya hai.
4808,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kuttey ki qeemat aur nar ki jufti ki ujrat leney sey mana farmaya hai.
4809,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs muflis qarar diya jaey, phir koi shakhs apna saman uskey paas waisa hi paa-ley to wo us saman ka dusron sey ziyada haq-daar hai."
4810,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs muflis qarar diya jaey, phir koi shakhs apna saman uskey paas waisa hi paa-ley to wo us saman ka dusron sey ziyada haq-daar hai."
4811,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney muflis aadmi key barey mein farmaya : jab uskey paas kisi ka saman wesa hi paya jaey aur is mein koi shak na rahey to wo uskey asal Malik ko dey diya jaeyga jisney usey bechaa tha. (ba-sharte-ke qeemat sey kuchh adaegi na hui ho).
4812,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney muflis aadmi key barey mein farmaya : jab uskey paas kisi ka saman wesa hi paya jaey aur is mein koi shak na rahey to wo uskey asal Malik ko dey diya jaeyga jisney usey bechaa tha. (ba-sharte-ke qeemat sey kuchh adaegi na hui ho).
4813,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daure-mubarak main eik aadmi key un phalon ka nuqsan ho gaya jo us ney khareedey they. is tarah is par bahut qarz chadh gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya is par sadqa karo. logon ney is par sadqa kiya magar us sey us ka pura qarz ada nahin ho sakta tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (us key qarz khuwahon sey) farmaya : jo milta hai ley lo, tumhein aur kuchh nahin milega."
4814,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daure-mubarak main eik aadmi key un phalon ka nuqsan ho gaya jo us ney khareedey they. is tarah is par bahut qarz chadh gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya is par sadqa karo. logon ney is par sadqa kiya magar us sey us ka pura qarz ada nahin ho sakta tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (us key qarz khuwahon sey) farmaya : jo milta hai ley lo, tumhein aur kuchh nahin milega."
4815,"Hazrat Usaid bin Huzer bin Samaak (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney faisla farmaya ke jab koi aadmi apni chiz aisey shakhs key haath mein paey jo mashkook aur muttahim (jis par jhoot wagheira ka ilzam laga ho) na ho, agar wo chahey to us sey wo chiz itni raqam dey kar jitni ki us ney khareedi hai ley ley. aur agar chahey to (asal) chor ka peechha kerey. Hazrat Abu-Bakar aur Hazrat umr Raziallahu anhuma ney bhi yehi faisla farmaya."
4816,"Hazrat Usaid bin Huzer bin Samaak (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney faisla farmaya ke jab koi aadmi apni chiz aisey shakhs key haath mein paey jo mashkook aur muttahim (jis par jhoot wagheira ka ilzam laga ho) na ho, agar wo chahey to us sey wo chiz itni raqam dey kar jitni ki us ney khareedi hai ley ley. aur agar chahey to (asal) chor ka peechha kerey. Hazrat Abu-Bakar aur Hazrat umr Raziallahu anhuma ney bhi yehi faisla farmaya."
4817,"Hazrat Usaid bin Zuher Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) jo ke Yamaama key governer they, ney bataya ke mujhey Hazrat Marwan ney likha ke Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ney mujhey likha hai ke jis aadmi ki koi chiz chori ho jaey, wo jahan bhi usey pa ley us ka ziyada haq daar hai. mainey in ko likha ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney faisla farmaya tha ke jab chor sey khareedney wala shakhs mashkook aur muttahim (jis par jhoot wagheira ka ilzam laga ho) na ho to us chiz key Malik ko ikhtiyar hai, chahey to qeemat dey kar wo chiz ley ley aur chahey to chor ka peechha kerey. phir Hazrat Abu-Bakar, umr aur Usman Raziallahu anhum ney bhi yehi faisla diya. Hazrat Marwan ney mera khat Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein bhej diya. Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ney Marwan ko likha ke tum ya Usaid mujh par faisla nafiz nahin kar saktey balke main apni hudoodey-khilaafat mein faisla nafiz karney ka adhikar rakhta hun, is liye tum merey hukm key mutabiq faisla karo. Hazrat Marwan ney Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ka khat mujhey bhej diya. mainey kaha : jab tak main governer hun main to Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) key is qol key mutabiq faisla nahin karunga."
4818,"Hazrat Usaid bin Zuher Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) jo ke Yamaama key governer they, ney bataya ke mujhey Hazrat Marwan ney likha ke Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ney mujhey likha hai ke jis aadmi ki koi chiz chori ho jaey, wo jahan bhi usey pa ley us ka ziyada haq daar hai. mainey in ko likha ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney faisla farmaya tha ke jab chor sey khareedney wala shakhs mashkook aur muttahim (jis par jhoot wagheira ka ilzam laga ho) na ho to us chiz key Malik ko ikhtiyar hai, chahey to qeemat dey kar wo chiz ley ley aur chahey to chor ka peechha kerey. phir Hazrat Abu-Bakar, umr aur Usman Raziallahu anhum ney bhi yehi faisla diya. Hazrat Marwan ney mera khat Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein bhej diya. Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ney Marwan ko likha ke tum ya Usaid mujh par faisla nafiz nahin kar saktey balke main apni hudoodey-khilaafat mein faisla nafiz karney ka adhikar rakhta hun, is liye tum merey hukm key mutabiq faisla karo. Hazrat Marwan ney Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ka khat mujhey bhej diya. mainey kaha : jab tak main governer hun main to Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) key is qol key mutabiq faisla nahin karunga."
4819,Hazrat Samura (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aadmi apney aen (asal) maal ka ziyada haq daar hai jab (aur jahan) bhi usey pa ley. khareedney wala khud bechney waley ka peechha karey.
4820,Hazrat Samura (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aadmi apney aen (asal) maal ka ziyada haq daar hai jab (aur jahan) bhi usey pa ley. khareedney wala khud bechney waley ka peechha karey.
4821,"Hazrat Samura (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis aurat ka nikah do wali (alag alag ) jagah kar den, wo us khawind ki hogi jis sey pehley nikah huwa. aur agar kisi shakhs ney eik chiz do aadmiyon ko (alag alag ) bech di to wo chiz us ko milegi jis ko pehley bechi gaee hai."
4822,"Hazrat Samura (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis aurat ka nikah do wali (alag alag ) jagah kar den, wo us khawind ki hogi jis sey pehley nikah huwa. aur agar kisi shakhs ney eik chiz do aadmiyon ko (alag alag ) bech di to wo chiz us ko milegi jis ko pehley bechi gaee hai."
4823,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abu-Rabeea (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey chaalis hazar (dirham) qarz liye, phir aap key paas kahin sey maal aaya. aap ney mera qarz merey supurd kiya aur farmaya : Allah Taala terey ehal aur maal mein barkat farmaey. qarz ka badla tareef aur adaegi hai."
4824,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abu-Rabeea (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey chaalis hazar (dirham) qarz liye, phir aap key paas kahin sey maal aaya. aap ney mera qarz merey supurd kiya aur farmaya : Allah Taala terey ehal aur maal mein barkat farmaey. qarz ka badla tareef aur adaegi hai."
4825,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Jahash (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas bethey they ke aap ney apna sar aasman ki taraf uthaya. phir apni hatheli apni peshani par rakhi, phir farmaya : Subhan-Allah ! kis qadr sakht hukm utra hai? hum khamosh rahey lekin ghabra gaey. agley din mainey puchha : aey Allah key Rasool ! wo kya sakht hukm tha? aap ney farmaya is zaat ki qism jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! agar koi aadmi Allah Taala key raastey mein shaheed kiya jaey, phir usey zinda kiya jaey, phir shaheed kiya jaey, phir zinda kiya jaey, phir shaheed kiya jaey jabkey uskey zimmey qarz wajibul-adaa ho to wo jannat mein dakhil nahin hoga yahan tak ke uskey zimmey wajibul-adaa qarz uski taraf sey ada kar diya jaey."
4826,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Jahash (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas bethey they ke aap ney apna sar aasman ki taraf uthaya. phir apni hatheli apni peshani par rakhi, phir farmaya : Subhan-Allah ! kis qadr sakht hukm utra hai? hum khamosh rahey lekin ghabra gaey. agley din mainey puchha : aey Allah key Rasool ! wo kya sakht hukm tha? aap ney farmaya is zaat ki qism jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! agar koi aadmi Allah Taala key raastey mein shaheed kiya jaey, phir usey zinda kiya jaey, phir shaheed kiya jaey, phir zinda kiya jaey, phir shaheed kiya jaey jabkey uskey zimmey qarz wajibul-adaa ho to wo jannat mein dakhil nahin hoga yahan tak ke uskey zimmey wajibul-adaa qarz uski taraf sey ada kar diya jaey."
4827,"Hazrat Samura (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hum Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath eik janaazey mein they. aap ney teen dafa farmaya : kya yahan falan khandan ka koi fard hai? aakhir eik aadmi khada huwa. aap ney usey farmaya : pehli do dafa tujhey kon si chiz jawab deney sey maanea' (rukaawat) thi? mainey tujhey eik achchhey maqsad key liye bulaya tha. is qabiley ka falan shakhs jo faut ho gaya tha, wo apney qarz ki wajeh sey giraftar hai."
4828,"Hazrat Samura (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hum Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath eik janaazey mein they. aap ney teen dafa farmaya : kya yahan falan khandan ka koi fard hai? aakhir eik aadmi khada huwa. aap ney usey farmaya : pehli do dafa tujhey kon si chiz jawab deney sey maanea' (rukaawat) thi? mainey tujhey eik achchhey maqsad key liye bulaya tha. is qabiley ka falan shakhs jo faut ho gaya tha, wo apney qarz ki wajeh sey giraftar hai."
4829,"Hazrat Imran bin Huzefa sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) qarz liya karti thin aur ziyada liya karti thin. unkey rishte-daaron ney is barey mein un par aetraz kiya, malamat ki aur naraz huye. wo farmaney lagin : main qarz lena nahin chhodungi kyonkey mainey apney piyarey mehbub khawind (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna hai : jo shakhs bhi qarz leta hai, jis key barey Allah Taala ko ilm ho ke wo adaegi ki niyat rakhta hai to Allah Taala duniya hi mein us ka qarz uski taraf sey ada kara dega."
4830,"Hazrat Imran bin Huzefa sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) qarz liya karti thin aur ziyada liya karti thin. unkey rishte-daaron ney is barey mein un par aetraz kiya, malamat ki aur naraz huye. wo farmaney lagin : main qarz lena nahin chhodungi kyonkey mainey apney piyarey mehbub khawind (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna hai : jo shakhs bhi qarz leta hai, jis key barey Allah Taala ko ilm ho ke wo adaegi ki niyat rakhta hai to Allah Taala duniya hi mein us ka qarz uski taraf sey ada kara dega."
4831,"Hazrat Ubedullah bin Abdullah bin Utba sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma (biwi) ney eik dafa qarz liya. un sey kaha gaya aey ummul-Mominin ! aap qarz leti hain jabkey aap key wapsi key liye kuchh bhi nahin? wo farmaney lagin : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jo shakhs qarz ley jabkey wo adaegi ka irada rakhta ho, Allah Taala uski madad farmata hai."
4832,"Hazrat Ubedullah bin Abdullah bin Utba sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma (biwi) ney eik dafa qarz liya. un sey kaha gaya aey ummul-Mominin ! aap qarz leti hain jabkey aap key wapsi key liye kuchh bhi nahin? wo farmaney lagin : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jo shakhs qarz ley jabkey wo adaegi ka irada rakhta ho, Allah Taala uski madad farmata hai."
4833,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey kisi (qarz khuwah) ko kisi maal daar shakhs key peechhey lagaya jaey to usey peechhey lag jana chahiye. (agar usey kisi maal-daar shakhs sey apna qarz wasul karney ki pesh kaash! ki jaey to wo ye pesh kaash! qubul kar ley). zulm ye hai ke maaldaar shakhs taal matol (adaegi mein takheer) karey.
4834,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey kisi (qarz khuwah) ko kisi maal daar shakhs key peechhey lagaya jaey to usey peechhey lag jana chahiye. (agar usey kisi maal-daar shakhs sey apna qarz wasul karney ki pesh kaash! ki jaey to wo ye pesh kaash! qubul kar ley). zulm ye hai ke maaldaar shakhs taal matol (adaegi mein takheer) karey.
4835,Hazrat Shareed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : adaegi ki gunjaaish rakhney wala shakhs adaegi mein taal matol karey to uski be-izzati ki ja sakti hai aur usey saza bhi di ja sakti hai.
4836,Hazrat Shareed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : adaegi ki gunjaaish rakhney wala shakhs adaegi mein taal matol karey to uski be-izzati ki ja sakti hai aur usey saza bhi di ja sakti hai.
4837,Hazrat Shareed (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : maaldaar shakhs (adaegi mein) heeley bahaney karey to uski be-izzati karna aur usey saza dena jayez aur halal hai.
4838,Hazrat Shareed (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : maaldaar shakhs (adaegi mein) heeley bahaney karey to uski be-izzati karna aur usey saza dena jayez aur halal hai.
4839,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sahibe-istataat shakhs ka adaegi sey taal matol karna zulm hai. aur jab kisi (qarz khuwah) ko kisi maaldaar shakhs key supurd kiya jaey to usey chahiye ke wo adaegi key liye us sey ruju kerey.
4840,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sahibe-istataat shakhs ka adaegi sey taal matol karna zulm hai. aur jab kisi (qarz khuwah) ko kisi maaldaar shakhs key supurd kiya jaey to usey chahiye ke wo adaegi key liye us sey ruju kerey.
4841,Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke eik Ansari shakhs ka janaza Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein laya gaya ke aap us ka janaza padhaen. aap ney farmaya : tumharey is sathi key zimmey to qarz hai. Abu-Qatada ney kaha : uski adaegi ka main zimme-daar banta hun. aap ney farmaya : pura ada karogey? mainey kaha : pura (ada karunga).
4842,Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke eik Ansari shakhs ka janaza Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein laya gaya ke aap us ka janaza padhaen. aap ney farmaya : tumharey is sathi key zimmey to qarz hai. Abu-Qatada ney kaha : uski adaegi ka main zimme-daar banta hun. aap ney farmaya : pura ada karogey? mainey kaha : pura (ada karunga).
4843,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey behtareen wo log hain jo adaegi karney mein achchhey hon.
4844,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey behtareen wo log hain jo adaegi karney mein achchhey hon.
4845,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik aadmi ney kabhi neki nahin ki thi. wo logon sey len-den kiya karta tha. wo apney karindey sey kehta tha ke jo aasani sey mohaiyya ho sakey, ley lena aur jis mein maqrooz ko tangi ho, wo chhod dena balke maaf kar dena. ummid hai Allah Taala bhi hamein maaf kerega, phir jab wo faut ho gaya to Allah Taala ney usey farmaya : kya tu ney kabhi koi neki ki hai? us ney kaha : nahin, magar mera eik ghulam tha aur main logon sey len-den kiya karta tha. jab main usey wasuli key liye bhejta tha to main usey kehta tha : jo aasani sey mil jaey, ley lena aur jis mein deney waley ko tangi ho, chhod dena aur maaf kar dena. shayad Allah Taala hamein maaf farma dey. Allah Taala ney farmaya : ja mainey tujhey maaf kar diya."
4846,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik aadmi ney kabhi neki nahin ki thi. wo logon sey len-den kiya karta tha. wo apney karindey sey kehta tha ke jo aasani sey mohaiyya ho sakey, ley lena aur jis mein maqrooz ko tangi ho, wo chhod dena balke maaf kar dena. ummid hai Allah Taala bhi hamein maaf kerega, phir jab wo faut ho gaya to Allah Taala ney usey farmaya : kya tu ney kabhi koi neki ki hai? us ney kaha : nahin, magar mera eik ghulam tha aur main logon sey len-den kiya karta tha. jab main usey wasuli key liye bhejta tha to main usey kehta tha : jo aasani sey mil jaey, ley lena aur jis mein deney waley ko tangi ho, chhod dena aur maaf kar dena. shayad Allah Taala hamein maaf farma dey. Allah Taala ney farmaya : ja mainey tujhey maaf kar diya."
4847,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik aadmi logon sey len-den kiya karta tha. jab wo kisi tang dast ki tang dasti dekhta to apney naukar sey kehta tha ke usey maaf kar do shayad Allah Taala hamein maaf kar dey. phir (wafat key baad) wo shakhs Allah Taala key samney hazir huwa to Allah Taala ney usey maaf farma diya.
4848,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik aadmi logon sey len-den kiya karta tha. jab wo kisi tang dast ki tang dasti dekhta to apney naukar sey kehta tha ke usey maaf kar do shayad Allah Taala hamein maaf kar dey. phir (wafat key baad) wo shakhs Allah Taala key samney hazir huwa to Allah Taala ney usey maaf farma diya.
4849,"Hazrat Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney eik aadmi ko is bina par jannat mein dakhil kar diya ke wo khareedtey, bechtey, ada kartey aur talab kartey waqt naram ravaiya rakhta tha."
4850,"Hazrat Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney eik aadmi ko is bina par jannat mein dakhil kar diya ke wo khareedtey, bechtey, ada kartey aur talab kartey waqt naram ravaiya rakhta tha."
4851,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main, Ammaar aur Saad Badr key din shareek baney. Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) do qaidi laye. main aur Ammaar kuchh na laye."
4852,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main, Ammaar aur Saad Badr key din shareek baney. Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) do qaidi laye. main aur Ammaar kuchh na laye."
4853,Hazrat Salim key walid mohtaram (Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs kisi ghulam mein apna hissa azad kar dey to baqi hissey ki azadi bhi uskey maal sey hogi ba-sharte-ke uskey paas itna maal ho jo us ghulam ki qeemat key barabar ho.
4854,Hazrat Salim key walid mohtaram (Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs kisi ghulam mein apna hissa azad kar dey to baqi hissey ki azadi bhi uskey maal sey hogi ba-sharte-ke uskey paas itna maal ho jo us ghulam ki qeemat key barabar ho.
4855,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs kisi ghulam mein apna hissa azad kar dey aur uskey paas itna maal ho jo us ghulam key baqi hissey ki qeemat ban sakey to wo ghulam (purey ka pura) uskey maal sey azad hoga.
4856,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs kisi ghulam mein apna hissa azad kar dey aur uskey paas itna maal ho jo us ghulam key baqi hissey ki qeemat ban sakey to wo ghulam (purey ka pura) uskey maal sey azad hoga.
4857,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey jis shakhs key paas zamin ya khajuron key darkht hon to wo unhein na bechey yahan tak ke apney shareek par pesh karey (apney shareek ko khareedney ki paish-kash karey).
4858,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey jis shakhs key paas zamin ya khajuron key darkht hon to wo unhein na bechey yahan tak ke apney shareek par pesh karey (apney shareek ko khareedney ki paish-kash karey).
4859,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney har mushtarak chiz mein shuf'a ka haq qarar diya hai ba-sharte-ke wo taqseem na hui ho. ghar ho ya khet ho ya baagh. kisi eik shareek ko apna hissa bechney ki ijazat nahin yahan tak ke apney shareek ko muttala (ittila) karey. chahey wo ley ley, chahey na ley. lekin agar usey ittilaa kiye baghair bech dala to shareek us ka ziyada haq-daar hoga."
4860,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney har mushtarak chiz mein shuf'a ka haq qarar diya hai ba-sharte-ke wo taqseem na hui ho. ghar ho ya khet ho ya baagh. kisi eik shareek ko apna hissa bechney ki ijazat nahin yahan tak ke apney shareek ko muttala (ittila) karey. chahey wo ley ley, chahey na ley. lekin agar usey ittilaa kiye baghair bech dala to shareek us ka ziyada haq-daar hoga."
4861,Hazrat Abu-Raafea' (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : padosi apney qurb (nazdeeki) ki wajeh sey ziyada haq rakhta hai.
4862,Hazrat Abu-Raafea' (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : padosi apney qurb (nazdeeki) ki wajeh sey ziyada haq rakhta hai.
4863,"Hazrat Shareed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! meri zamin mein koi shakhs shareek nahin, na kisi ka hissa hai, albatta padaus hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : padosi bhi qurb (nazdeeki) ki wajeh sey haq-daar hai."
4864,"Hazrat Shareed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! meri zamin mein koi shakhs shareek nahin, na kisi ka hissa hai, albatta padaus hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : padosi bhi qurb (nazdeeki) ki wajeh sey haq-daar hai."
4865,Hazrat abu-Salma sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : shuf'a har us maal mein hai jo taqseem na huwa ho. jab alag alag had bandi ho jaey aur raastey bhi alag alag ho jaaeyn to shuf'a baqi nahin rehta.
4866,Hazrat abu-Salma sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : shuf'a har us maal mein hai jo taqseem na huwa ho. jab alag alag had bandi ho jaey aur raastey bhi alag alag ho jaaeyn to shuf'a baqi nahin rehta.
4867,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney shuf'a aur padaus key haq ko barqarar rakha hai.
4868,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney shuf'a aur padaus key haq ko barqarar rakha hai.
4869,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jahiliyat mein sab sey pehli qasamat is tarah hui ke banu Haashim mein sey eik aadmi ko kisi dusrey qabiley key eik quraishi ney ujrat par apney paas rakha. wo naukar us quraishi key sath uskey oonton mein gaya. ittifaaq se banu Haashim ka eik aadmi uskey paas sey guzra. uskey borey key munh ki rassi toot chuki thi. us ney Haashmi naukar sey kaha : mujhey eik rassi do jis sey main apney borey ka munh baandh lun taake oont na ghabraaeyn. us naukar ney usey eik oont ki ghutna baandhney wali rassi dey di taake wo apney borey ka munh baandh ley. jab wo aagey ja kar kisi manzil mein utrey aur oonton key ghutney baandhey gaey to eik oont khula reh gaya. Malik ney kaha : kya wajeh hai ke us eik oont ka ghutna nahin baandha gaya? us ney kaha : uski rassi nahin. us ney kaha : uski rassi kidhar gaee? us ney bataya ke merey paas sey banu Haashim ka eik aadmi guzra tha. uskey borey key munh wali rassi toot chuki thi. us ney mujh sey madad talab ki aur kaha ke mujhey eik rassi dey jis key sath mein apney borey ka munh baandh lun taake oont na ghabraaeyn. mainey us ko dey di. Malik ney (ghussey mein) uski taraf zor sey lathi phenki jo uski maut ka baais ban gaee. (woh qaribul-maut tha ke) itney mein udhar sey eik Yamni aadmi guzra. us (Haashmi naukar) ney Yamni sey kaha : kya to mausamey-hajj mein (Makka Mukarrama) jata hai? us ney kaha : aam to nahin jata, kabhi kabhar jata hun. us ney kaha : kya to apni sari umr mein kisi bhi waqt mera ye pegham pahunchaeyga? us ney kaha : zarur. us ney kaha : jab to mausame-hajj mein jaey to aelan karna : aey Quraishiyon ! jab wo aa jaeyn to banu Haashim key barey mein poochhnaa, phir jab wo aa jaeyn to Abu Talib key barey mein poochhnaa aur usey batana ke falan shakhs ney mujhey eik rassi ki wajeh sey qatl kar diya hai. (itni baat keh kar) wo naukar mar gaya. jab wo shakhs wapis (Makkey) aaya jisney usey naukar rakha tha to Abu Talib uskey paas gaey aur puchha : hamarey aadmi ka kya bana? us ney kaha : wo (raastey mein) bimar ho gaya tha. mainey uski khub teemaardaari ki magar wo faut ho gaya. mainey padaaw kiya aur us ka kafan dafn kiya. wo kehney lagey : waqae wo tujh sey isi sulook ka ehal tha. phir kuchh arsa guzra to wo Yamni shakhs jisey us naukar ney wasiyat ki thi ke ye pegham pahunchaey, mausame-hajj mein aa gaya. us ney aelan kiya : aey Quraishiyon ! logon ney kaha : ye Quraishi hain. phir us ney kaha : aey Haashmiyo ! logon ney kaha : ye Haashmi hain. us ney kaha : Abu Talib kahan hain? kisi ney kaha : ye Abu Talib hain. us ney kaha : mujhey falan shakhs ney kaha tha ke main tujhey ye pegham pahuncha dun ke falan shakhs ney usey eik rassi ki bina par qatl kiya hai. tab Abu Talib us (qatil) key paas aaye aur kaha : hamari taraf sey teen baaton mein sey koi eik qubul kar ley : agar to chahey to sau oont bator diyat ada kar kyonkey tu ney hamara aadmi ghalati sey qatl kiya hai. agar to chahey to teri qom key pachas aadmi qism khaeyn ke tu ney usey qatl nahin kiya. agar to in dono baaton ko taslim nahin kerega to hum tujhey uskey badley qatl kar dengey. wo apni qom key paas gaya aur un sey ye sari baat zikr ki. unhoney kaha : hum qasmen khaeyngey. banu Haashim ki eik aurat jo us qabiley key eik aadmi key nikah mein thi aur us sey uski aulad bhi thi, Abu Talib key paas aai aur kehney lagi : Abu Talib ! main chahti hun ke to merey betey ko pachas aadmiyon par padney wali qism maaf kar dey aur us sey qism na ley. Abu Talib maan gaey. us qabiley mein sey eik aur aadmi aaya aur kehney laga : Abu Talib ! to sau oonton key iwaz pachas aadmiyon sey qasmen lena chahta hai. is lihaz sey har aadmi ko do oont padtey hain. ye do oont meri taraf sey qubul kar ley aur jab qasmen li jaeyn to meri qism na li jaey. Abu Talib ney do oont ley liye. baqi adtaalis (48) aadmi aaye aur unhoney qasmen khaeyn. Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke qism us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! abhi pura saal bhi nahin guzra tha ke un (48) aadmiyon mein sey koi eik aankh harkat karti ho. (sarey key sarey mar gaey)."
4870,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jahiliyat mein sab sey pehli qasamat is tarah hui ke banu Haashim mein sey eik aadmi ko kisi dusrey qabiley key eik quraishi ney ujrat par apney paas rakha. wo naukar us quraishi key sath uskey oonton mein gaya. ittifaaq se banu Haashim ka eik aadmi uskey paas sey guzra. uskey borey key munh ki rassi toot chuki thi. us ney Haashmi naukar sey kaha : mujhey eik rassi do jis sey main apney borey ka munh baandh lun taake oont na ghabraaeyn. us naukar ney usey eik oont ki ghutna baandhney wali rassi dey di taake wo apney borey ka munh baandh ley. jab wo aagey ja kar kisi manzil mein utrey aur oonton key ghutney baandhey gaey to eik oont khula reh gaya. Malik ney kaha : kya wajeh hai ke us eik oont ka ghutna nahin baandha gaya? us ney kaha : uski rassi nahin. us ney kaha : uski rassi kidhar gaee? us ney bataya ke merey paas sey banu Haashim ka eik aadmi guzra tha. uskey borey key munh wali rassi toot chuki thi. us ney mujh sey madad talab ki aur kaha ke mujhey eik rassi dey jis key sath mein apney borey ka munh baandh lun taake oont na ghabraaeyn. mainey us ko dey di. Malik ney (ghussey mein) uski taraf zor sey lathi phenki jo uski maut ka baais ban gaee. (woh qaribul-maut tha ke) itney mein udhar sey eik Yamni aadmi guzra. us (Haashmi naukar) ney Yamni sey kaha : kya to mausamey-hajj mein (Makka Mukarrama) jata hai? us ney kaha : aam to nahin jata, kabhi kabhar jata hun. us ney kaha : kya to apni sari umr mein kisi bhi waqt mera ye pegham pahunchaeyga? us ney kaha : zarur. us ney kaha : jab to mausame-hajj mein jaey to aelan karna : aey Quraishiyon ! jab wo aa jaeyn to banu Haashim key barey mein poochhnaa, phir jab wo aa jaeyn to Abu Talib key barey mein poochhnaa aur usey batana ke falan shakhs ney mujhey eik rassi ki wajeh sey qatl kar diya hai. (itni baat keh kar) wo naukar mar gaya. jab wo shakhs wapis (Makkey) aaya jisney usey naukar rakha tha to Abu Talib uskey paas gaey aur puchha : hamarey aadmi ka kya bana? us ney kaha : wo (raastey mein) bimar ho gaya tha. mainey uski khub teemaardaari ki magar wo faut ho gaya. mainey padaaw kiya aur us ka kafan dafn kiya. wo kehney lagey : waqae wo tujh sey isi sulook ka ehal tha. phir kuchh arsa guzra to wo Yamni shakhs jisey us naukar ney wasiyat ki thi ke ye pegham pahunchaey, mausame-hajj mein aa gaya. us ney aelan kiya : aey Quraishiyon ! logon ney kaha : ye Quraishi hain. phir us ney kaha : aey Haashmiyo ! logon ney kaha : ye Haashmi hain. us ney kaha : Abu Talib kahan hain? kisi ney kaha : ye Abu Talib hain. us ney kaha : mujhey falan shakhs ney kaha tha ke main tujhey ye pegham pahuncha dun ke falan shakhs ney usey eik rassi ki bina par qatl kiya hai. tab Abu Talib us (qatil) key paas aaye aur kaha : hamari taraf sey teen baaton mein sey koi eik qubul kar ley : agar to chahey to sau oont bator diyat ada kar kyonkey tu ney hamara aadmi ghalati sey qatl kiya hai. agar to chahey to teri qom key pachas aadmi qism khaeyn ke tu ney usey qatl nahin kiya. agar to in dono baaton ko taslim nahin kerega to hum tujhey uskey badley qatl kar dengey. wo apni qom key paas gaya aur un sey ye sari baat zikr ki. unhoney kaha : hum qasmen khaeyngey. banu Haashim ki eik aurat jo us qabiley key eik aadmi key nikah mein thi aur us sey uski aulad bhi thi, Abu Talib key paas aai aur kehney lagi : Abu Talib ! main chahti hun ke to merey betey ko pachas aadmiyon par padney wali qism maaf kar dey aur us sey qism na ley. Abu Talib maan gaey. us qabiley mein sey eik aur aadmi aaya aur kehney laga : Abu Talib ! to sau oonton key iwaz pachas aadmiyon sey qasmen lena chahta hai. is lihaz sey har aadmi ko do oont padtey hain. ye do oont meri taraf sey qubul kar ley aur jab qasmen li jaeyn to meri qism na li jaey. Abu Talib ney do oont ley liye. baqi adtaalis (48) aadmi aaye aur unhoney qasmen khaeyn. Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke qism us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! abhi pura saal bhi nahin guzra tha ke un (48) aadmiyon mein sey koi eik aankh harkat karti ho. (sarey key sarey mar gaey)."
4871,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key eik Ansari sahabi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney qasamat ko barqarar rakha hai jaisey ke wo jahiliyat mein raaij thi.
4872,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key eik Ansari sahabi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney qasamat ko barqarar rakha hai jaisey ke wo jahiliyat mein raaij thi.
4873,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key bahut sey sahaba sey riwayat hai ke qasamat jahiliyat mein raaij thi. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney isey isi tarah barqarar rakha jis tarah ye jahiliyat mein thi aur aap ney eik maqtool key barey mein qasamat ka faisla bhi kiya tha jis key qatl ka ilzam ansaar ney khaiber key yahudiyon par lagaya tha. Maamar ney in dono ki mukhalifat ki hai.
